messages.content: ComfyUI-Video-Matting is a minimalistic implementation of Robust Video Matting (RVM) and BRAIAI-RVMBG v1.4 in ComfyUI.
Robust Video Matting (RVM) is a video matting technique that has been implemented in ComfyUI-Video-Matting.
BRAIAI-RVMBG v1.4 is a background removal technique that has been implemented in ComfyUI-Video-Matting.
Is there an example workflow available for ComfyUI-Video-Matting?
Yes, there is an example workflow available for ComfyUI-Video-Matting, which can be found in the 'example_matting_workflow.json' file.
Are there any visual examples of ComfyUI-Video-Matting?

Yes, there are visual examples of ComfyUI-Video-Matting available. One example can be found at the provided GitHub link: https://github.com/Fannovel16/ComfyUI-Video-Matting/assets/16047777/aa545ace-efdd-425b-b8b3-940274d1f851.
Are there any visual examples of BRAIAI implementation in ComfyUI-Video-Matting?

Yes, there is a visual example of BRAIAI implementation in ComfyUI-Video-Matting available at the provided GitHub link: https://github.com/Fannovel16/ComfyUI-Video-Matting/assets/16047777/c0bf92b6-a098-4197-808c-f9a8b4f61af2.
Where can I find the code repository for ComfyUI-Video-Matting?
The code repository for ComfyUI-Video-Matting can be found on GitHub at https://github.com/Fannovel16/ComfyUI-Video-Matting.
